snippet.textDisplay: Figures from Israel indicate that protection by the Pfizer vaccine against infection is waning, with percentages in the high 30's being reported as an average across the sample group.  Protection percentages are in the high teens for the earliest vaccinated in the sample.  Protection against severe disease, and hospital admission, have reportedly remained in the 90's, thankfully.  Antibodies fading, but T Cells reacting and stimulating antibody production once infection occurs???  My data source - Dr John Campbell.
